Usage: FORMAT SEND_LOCOPS <format description>
  Controls how locops appear when sent

  Valid format characters:
       F          Nick of person sending message (your nick)
       M          The message
       O          Replaced by "*" if person sending message is an operator

See Also:
  LOCOPS
